list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Add initial styles, blog post tutorial, translations, and assets
This commit introduces foundational CSS for homepage features, blog post creation tutorials, support for site translations, and accompanying static assets such as images and configuration files. These updates are key for improving site appearance, multi-language support, and user guidance.

Update site localization and content for English-only support
Replaced Danish localization with English as the default and sole language across the site. Updated all labels, navigation, and content to reflect the new language focus, including the introduction of new English documentation and blog author configuration.

Improve Docusaurus setup script in deploy workflow
Added non-interactive flags to streamline Docusaurus creation and improved file copying to handle hidden files. Included listing of temporary directory contents for better debugging. These changes enhance robustness and clarity in the deployment process.

Revise Docusaurus setup to resolve installation issues
Updated the Docusaurus installation script to remove problematic arguments causing errors and added safeguards for handling the temp directory. Improved backup and cleanup steps, ensuring stability and robustness during deployments.
